        public SecurityProperties(org.apache.cxf.message.Message message)
        Deprecated. use SecurityUtils.getSubject()
        Looks for the Subject object from the incoming CXF message. If available (should have been added by the interceptors) it adds the subject to this map so that it can be added to the query request.
        Parameters:
        message - Incoming CXF message that may contain a subject
